                  <interp inst="t18281204-11-crimeloc61" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-11-off58 t18281204-11-crimeloc61"></join>. On the 1st of December, about nine o'clock at night, these shoes hung at the door, within reach of a person passing; I heard something snatched down, turned round, and my lad said a pair of shoes were gone - I pursued up Harp-alley, and took the prisioner; I opened his jacket, and asked him where the shoes were - he said, "What shoes?" my lad said they were behind him, and I took them up.</p>
